Others: The USA will play against Nepal in a three-match T20I series starting on October 18.
Monank Patel will captain the USA side, with Andries Gous and Aaron Jones as experienced batters.
Harmeet Singh, Saurabh Netravalkar, and Nosthusha Kenjige are the key bowlers for the USA.
Rohit Paudel will lead Nepal with support from Sandeep Lamichhane, Dipendra Singh Airee, and Sompal Kami.
The series will be hosted at the Grand Prairie Stadium in Dallas.
